Package: multibayes
Type: Package
Title: Prior-Odds Adjustment for Probability of Direction
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Margherita", "Calderan", 
           email = "margherita.calderan@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-5668-5162"))
Description: Provides methods for Bayesian multiplicity adjustment using 
    probability of direction (pd) values. The main function adjusts pd values 
    using a global prior probability that all tested hypotheses are null, 
    converting it into per-hypothesis prior odds that account for family size. 
    This approach offers a principled framework for controlling multiplicity 
    in Bayesian inference while maintaining interpretability.
